1. Unit test: showSpinner returns handle with ID
2. Unit test: updateSpinner calls UiContext
3. Unit test: showProgress returns handle
4. Unit test: notifications dispatch correctly
5. Unit test: askUser resolves with answer
6. Integration test: Full JS to Rust flow

